### ATUALIZAR USUÁRIO
PUT http://localhost:3000/usuarios/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nome": "Israell Atualizado",
    "email": "israel@email.com",
    "senha": "123"
}

###

### REMOVER USUÁRIO
DELETE http://localhost:3000/usuarios/1